and a 1/10,000 viability.

00:41:01.700 --> 00:41:04.340
Here, these are two
different preparations.

00:41:04.340 --> 00:41:06.990
This preparation is obviously much better.

00:41:06.990 --> 00:41:09.330
And that's what we're
working on at the moment.

00:41:09.330 --> 00:41:10.970
This is at five micromolar

00:41:11.920 --> 00:41:13.320
concentration

00:41:13.320 --> 00:41:15.560
of the particular
compound that I worked on,

00:41:15.560 --> 00:41:16.783
that I told you about.

00:41:18.240 --> 00:41:22.020
So that's a summary of
some of our recent data.

